      <title>GIP 计划募集 30 亿美元用于新基础设施债务基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/gip-targets-3-billion-for-new-infrastructure-debt-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，全球基础设施合作伙伴（GIP）计划募集 30 亿美元用于成立一个新的基础设施债务基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/gip-targets-3-billion-for-new-infrastructure-debt-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 13:46:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
