      <title>亿万富翁的现金热潮有望推翻民主党的关键参议员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/montana-senate-rush-of-billionaire-cash-poised-to-topple-democrat-jon-tester</link>
